OL,3,C'They were equal' - The women at the
OL,4,Ccoalface of the miners' strike
OL,6,F"They know what they're capable of
OL,7,Fdoing and that's the thing for me that
OL,8,Flives on, I hope that if we work
OL,9,Ftogether we 'can do'."
OL,11,FHeather and her contemporaries hope
OL,12,Fthe part they played, and continue to
OL,13,Fplay, will inspire the future
OL,14,Fgenerations to make a stand.
